Achievements.Name: Exercise
Achievements.Description: Complete 10 Match the Pose jumps.

Achievements.Description: Collect 40 coins in one level on any Kayaking, Biking or Wave Riding level.

Achievements.Description: Pick a female character and use her to pass all activities at least once.

Achievements.Description: Collect 10 diamonds across all activities.

Achievements.Description: Finish any Biking level without falling from the bicycle.

Achievements.Name: Upright
Achievements.Description: Finish any Kayaking level without flipping the kayak.

Achievements.Name: Camp Star
Achievements.Description: Win the Cabela's Cup.

Achievements.Name: Speed Wheeler
Achievements.Description: Pass Biking 1 under 1 minute 10 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Shoot the Rapids
Achievements.Description: Pass Kayaking 1 under 1 minute 30 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Speed Cruiser
Achievements.Description: Pass Wave Riding 1 under 1 minute 30 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Flying Fish
Achievements.Description: Jump 15 times in Wave Riding 1 or 2.

Achievements.Description: Finish any shooting activity with a full 200 point accuracy bonus.

Achievements.Name: Speed Ace
Achievements.Description: Receive golden medals in all racing activities.
